## causal-net.core 
This package provides:

### causalNetCore

Allow acess to core functor and core tensor instance.

```javascript
import { causalNetCore } from 'causal-net.core';
console.log(causalNetCore.CoreTensor);
console.log(causalNetCore.CoreFunctor);

```

[Run code](./asset/examples/core.babel.js)

### Tensor

Primitive class for composing Tensor based class. This class is based on [tensorflowjs](https://js.tensorflow.org/)

```javascript
import { Tensor, causalNetCore } from 'causal-net.core';
let tensor = new Tensor();
let T = causalNetCore.CoreTensor;
let ta = T.tensor([1, 2]);
console.log(tensor.isTensor(ta));
console.log(tensor.isTensor([1,2,3]));
```

[Run code](./asset/examples/tensor.babel.js)

### Functor

Primitive class for composing Functor based class. This class is based on [Ramda](https://ramdajs.com/)

```javascript
import { Functor } from 'causal-net.core';

(async ()=>{
    let functor = new Functor();
    console.log(functor.range(10));
})();
```

[Run code](./asset/examples/functor.babel.js)

### Store

Primivtive class for composing Store base class. This class is based on [levelup](https://www.npmjs.com/package/levelup)

### Event

Primivtive class for composing Event base class. This class is extended from [EventEmitter](https://nodejs.org/api/events.html)

```javascript
import { Event } from 'causal-net.core';

(async ()=>{
    let eventA = new Event();
    let eventB = new Event();    
    eventA.on('data', (data)=>{
        console.log({'event handler': data});
        return 'this is done';
    })
    console.log(await eventA.emit('data', [1,2,3]));
    console.log('send event');
    eventB.pipe(eventA);
    console.log(await eventB.emit('data', ['1,2,3']));
})();

```

